CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 12, 1957, pg. 17, reads: "Westinghouse High School's Cheerleaders Are Sharp, Hard-Working Morale Boosters - 'Bulldog' Morale Boosters - As Westinghouse High School attempts to excel again in sports this year, the Bulldog teams are being inspired by a student body fired up by (left to right) cheerleaders Pat DeMauro, Diane Gardner, Donna Barclay, Alvinia Holt, Carole Waddy and Juanita Santillo. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Six Westinghouse High School cheerleaders, from left: Juanita Santillo, Carol or Carole Waddy, Donna Barclay or Barkley, Alvinia Holt, Diane Gardner, Pat DeMauro, standing on steps with pom poms
